original: Öhrstam, Gunnar Johan Ernst, apotekare, Ödeshög, f. 10/7/92 i Ör, Kro-nob. 1. G. 27 m. Ebba Sofia Nilsson. Barn: Torsten Karl Gunnar f. 27, Erik Ernst Gunnar 29. — Studiex. i Växjö 18, farm. kand. 22, apot :ex. 27. Elev v. apot. Hjorten i Sthlm 19-21, anst. v. apot. i Alingsås o. Arvika, Fläkta Örn i Malimö, Lejonet i Sthllm samt Lejonet i Upps., priv. å apot. i Ödes-höig sed. 43’.
translated: Öhrstam, Gunnar Johan Ernst, pharmacist, Ödeshög, b. 10/7/92 in Ör, Kronoberg County. 1st marriage 27 with Ebba Sofia Nilsson. Children: Torsten Karl Gunnar b. 27, Erik Ernst Gunnar b. 29. — Graduated from Växjö College 18, earned a degree in pharmacy 22, passed the pharmacist examination in 27. Trainee at Hjorten Pharmacy in Stockholm 19-21, employed at pharmacies in Alingsås and Arvika, Fläkta Örn in Malmö, Lejonet in Stockholm and Lejonet in Uppsala. Self-employed at Ödeshög Pharmacy since 43'.
